processors.name: APIer - Extract DB data
processors.comments:
Old query for testing

SELECT TOP 50 'POST' AS Method ,
'{
  "RequirementId": "'+PCDT.CardholderId+'",
  "RequirementStatus": 99,
  "RequirementStatusCalculationSync": true,
  "sendORN": false
}' AS BODY
, 
'[{
"Content-Type" :"application/json111"
}]' AS Headers , 
'5' AS Delay ,
'https://demo6328191.mockable.io/PTest' AS URI
FROM Cardholders_Gen2..pay_CardholderDetailsTbl AS PCDT WITH (NOLOCK)
WHERE PCDT.CreateDate > GETDATE() - 10
